{{Documentation subpage}}
== Usage ==
<pre style="overflow:auto;">
{{geonameslink |gnid= |name= }}
</pre>

==Example==
{{nowiki template demo|code=<nowiki>[{{geonameslink|gnid=2082960|name=yellow%20river}} Yellow River] in [{{geonamesabout}} Geonames.org (cc-by)]</nowiki>}}

==See also==
* {{tl|geonamesabout}}

